   - Commercial use: Permitted ✅
   - Type: W3C Living Standard

2. CSS3 (W3C Standard)
   - License: W3C Software Notice and License
   - URL: https://www.w3.org/Consortium/Legal/2002/copyright-software-20021231
   - Commercial use: Permitted ✅
   - Type: W3C Living Standard

3. JavaScript (ECMAScript ES6+)
   - License: None (language standard, no license required)
   - Commercial use: Permitted ✅
   - Type: ECMA International Standard

EXTERNAL DEPENDENCIES:
----------------------

4. Inter Font (Google Fonts)
   - Provider: Google LLC
   - License: SIL Open Font License 1.1 (OFL-1.1)
   - URL: https://scripts.sil.org/OFL
   - Commercial use: Permitted ✅
   - Connection: CDN (https://fonts.googleapis.com)
   - License requirements: Automatically satisfied via Google Fonts

5. Schema.org Vocabulary
   - Provider: Schema.org (Google, Microsoft, Yahoo, Yandex)
   - License: Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 3.0 Unported
   - URL: https://schema.org/docs/terms.html
   - Commercial use: Permitted ✅
   - Usage: JSON-LD markup on pages

6. Open Graph Protocol
   - Provider: Meta (Facebook)
   - License: MIT License
   - URL: https://github.com/opengraphprotocol/specs
   - Commercial use: Permitted ✅
   - Usage: Meta tags on pages

7. Twitter Cards
   - Provider: Twitter (X Corp)
   - License: Open Standard
   - Commercial use: Permitted ✅
   - Usage: Meta tags on pages

STANDARDS:
----------

8. JSON-LD (JSON for Linking Data)
   - Standard: W3C Recommendation
   - License: W3C Software Notice and License
   - Commercial use: Permitted ✅

